{"opinion":{"isContribuable":false,"votes_total":21,"arguments_yes_count":0,"arguments_no_count":0,"id":510,"created_at":"2015-10-10T07:19:21+0200","updated_at":"2015-10-10T07:33:15+0200","body":"<p>Il parait n&eacute;cessaire dans un objectif de simplification des d&eacute;marches adminstratives de cr&eacute;er un dossier unique des usagers, utilisable par l&#39;administration.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>","versions_count":1,"sources_count":0,"arguments_count":0,"author":{"username":"personnaz","displayName":"personnaz","uniqueId":"personnaz","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/personnaz","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}},"type":{"id":86,"title":"Section 1","subtitle":"Ouverture des donn\u00e9es publiques","voteWidgetType":2,"votesHelpText":"Pensez-vous que cette proposition permet d'atteindre les objectifs pr\u00e9sent\u00e9s dans l\u2019explication de l\u2019article ?","commentSystem":2,"color":"blue","versionable":true,"sourceable":true,"votesThreshold":null,"votesThresholdHelpText":null},"sources":[],"arguments":[],"modals":[],"votes":[{"user":{"username":"Jeanne Varasco","displayName":"Jeanne Varasco","uniqueId":"jeannevarasco","isAdmin":false,"media":{"url":"\/media\/cache\/default_avatar\/default\/0001\/01\/139_default_avatar.jpg"},"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/jeannevarasco","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}},{"user":{"username":"L\u00e9onard Michelet","displayName":"L\u00e9onard Michelet","uniqueId":"leonardmichelet","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/leonardmichelet","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}},{"user":{"username":"Pierre Fontenille","displayName":"Pierre Fontenille","uniqueId":"pierrefontenille1","isAdmin":false,"media":{"url":"\/media\/cache\/default_avatar\/default\/0001\/01\/512_default_avatar.jpg"},"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/pierrefontenille1","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}},{"user":{"username":"Pauline Randon","displayName":"Pauline Randon","uniqueId":"paulinerandon","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/paulinerandon","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}},{"user":{"username":"William Quaranta","displayName":"William Quaranta","uniqueId":"williamquaranta","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/williamquaranta","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}}],"appendices":[{"body":"<p>Dans celui-ci tous les &eacute;l&eacute;ments donn&eacute;s par un usager pour le logement (demande de logement, demande d&#39;aide, DALO etc) , la CAF, les services sociaux, le service des impots, etc, seraient consultables sur une seule banque de donn&eacute;es. Les services en r&eacute;seaux de l&#39;administration pourraient le consulter, l&#39;enrichir, le modifier en fonction des &eacute;l&eacute;ments apport&eacute;s par tous les citoyens.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bien entendu, afin de pr&eacute;server la vie priv&eacute;e des usagers, ce dossier unique serait diffusable qu&#39;aux int&eacute;ress&eacute;s et &agrave; l&#39;administration publique.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cela implique une mise en r&eacute;seau de l&#39;ensemble des services de l&#39;Etat.<\/p>","type":{"title":"Explication de l'article"}}],"ranking":234,"is_trashed":false,"title":"Un dossier unique","votes_nok":1,"votes_ok":18,"votes_mitige":2,"_links":{"show":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-1-ouverture-des-donnees-publiques-1\/un-dossier-unique","edit"